name: 90s Jennifer Aniston
description:
90s Jennifer Aniston,
Part 1 of my f.r.i.e.n.d.s embedd series.

Trained from 20 images of Jennifer Aniston from 1990s to 2000
Default vector in 1.5 base seems to rely heavily on her older version which is why I felt the need to make this embedd.

Download the file and place it into stable-diffusion-web-ui>embeddings folder.
Then simply add JeAni69 as a part of your prompt and she'll appear, I hope
Will work with all models with SD 1.5 as a base.
